text: Posts: 5,846 Check this off my bucket list! My Son and I will be in Arizona for the Monday Night Game against the Ravens!! Will be arriving on Friday and will be looking to tailgate on Monday. We will be in the "F" parking lot green entry. Don't know what the hell that means. Also looking for a good spot to watch the Sunday games. Yeah Baby "Cardinals will not beat Cardinals" Bruce Arians
